.DT
query_details_for
Disk World creator help
query_details_for

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_details_for -  This method returns the details for a specified type of money.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed * query_details_for(string word)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - the money type to get the type for
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/money_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the details for a specified type of money.
It will return an array of the form:

.EP
.SP 5 5
({ "heads", "tails", "a head", "a tail", "brass", 0 })
.EP
.SP 5 5
The places correspond to: 
.EP
.SP 5 5
({ forward short, reverse short,
.EP
.SP 5 5
     forward long, reverse long, composition, plural })
.EP
.SP 5 5

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_details()

.EP

